metadata.name: Rear Up
metadata.description:
I took the picture in Kayseri/Hürmetçi Reeds in August. Almost 400 jades were galloping around freely. I was running after the herd with great excitement. 
Artist: Nimet Gonenc Cinaroglu
Camera: NIKON D750
Date: 2017
Image Size: 5274 × 3516
Edition: 1/1
Location: Kayseri / Türkiye
